flowchart LR
    subgraph Mobile["Flutter mobile app"]
        ProductUI["<<component>> Product UI"]
        DevWrapper["<<component>> Codex dev wrapper"]
        SddPanel["<<component>> SDD visual panel"]
        FeedbackCapture["<<component>> Feedback capture"]
    end

    subgraph Backend["FastAPI bridge backend"]
        SddRoutes["<<component>> Read-only SDD routes"]
        FeedbackRoutes["<<component>> Feedback routes"]
        ActionRoutes["<<component>> Codex action routes"]
        SddService["<<component>> SddProjectService"]
        Config["<<component>> Real release config"]
    end

    subgraph Workspace["Current project workspace"]
        Manifest["<<component>> codex-bridge.yaml"]
        Constitution["<<component>> Constitution"]
        Specs["<<component>> Specs, plans, tasks"]
        Diagrams["<<component>> Mermaid diagrams"]
    end

    subgraph Tooling["Developer tooling"]
        CodexCli["<<component>> Codex CLI"]
        Doctor["<<component>> SDD doctor"]
        GitHubRelease["<<component>> Android release workflow"]
    end

    ProductUI -->|Flutter builder| DevWrapper
    DevWrapper -->|Workbench entry| SddPanel
    SddPanel -->|HTTP SDD API| SddRoutes
    FeedbackCapture -->|HTTP feedback API| FeedbackRoutes
    SddRoutes -->|service call| SddService
    SddService -->|file read| Manifest
    SddService -->|file read| Constitution
    SddService -->|file read| Specs
    SddService -->|file read| Diagrams
    ActionRoutes -->|Codex workflow| CodexCli
    ActionRoutes -->|doctor command| Doctor
    Config -->|release inputs| GitHubRelease

    %% UML interface orientation: consumer is on the circle side; provider is on the C/socket side.
    %% uml-interface: Flutter builder consumer=ProductUI provider=DevWrapper
    %% uml-interface: Workbench entry consumer=DevWrapper provider=SddPanel
    %% uml-interface: HTTP SDD API consumer=SddPanel provider=SddRoutes
    %% uml-interface: HTTP feedback API consumer=FeedbackCapture provider=FeedbackRoutes
    %% uml-interface: service call consumer=SddRoutes provider=SddService
    %% uml-interface: Codex workflow consumer=ActionRoutes provider=CodexCli
